values ('20','PUBG','PlayerUnknowns Battlegrounds is an online multiplayer battle royale game developed by PUBG Corporation. The game is based on previous mods that were created by Brendan "PlayerUnknown" Greene for other games, inspired by the 2000 Japanese film Battle Royale, and expanded into a standalone game under Greenes creative direction. In the game, up to one hundred players parachute onto an island and scavenge for weapons and equipment to kill others while avoiding getting killed themselves. The available safe area of the games map decreases in size over time, directing surviving players into tighter areas to force encounters. The last player or team standing wins the round.',to_date('16/09/12','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/PUBG.png','1','52','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','5','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/Pubg.mp4','Fay-Fritsch','15','FPS','/GameProfileImages/pubg.jpg');
values ('19','Witcher 3','The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt[a] is an action role-playing game developed and published by Polish developer CD Projekt Red and is based on The Witcher series of fantasy novels written by Andrzej Sapkowski. It is the sequel to the 2011 game The Witcher 2: Assassins of Kings and the third main installment in The Witcher video game series, played in an open world with a third-person perspective.',to_date('24/07/11','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/witcher3.png','7','10','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','3','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','1','Videos/Witcher3.mp4','Stracke, Block and Vandervort','15','RPG','/GameProfileImages/witcher3.jpg');
values ('1','Ac Valhalla','Assassins Creed Valhalla is a 2020 action role-playing video game developed by Ubisoft Montreal and published by Ubisoft. It is the twelfth major installment and the twenty-second release in the Assassins Creed series, and a successor to the 2018s Assassins Creed Odyssey. Principally set in the years 872ñ878 AD, the game recounts a fictional story during the Viking invasion of Britain. The player controls Eivor, a Viking raider who becomes embroiled in the conflict between the Assassin Brotherhood and the Templar Order.',to_date('20/05/10','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/ACValhalla.jpg','8','95','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','8','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/AcValhalla.mp4','Von, Hermiston and Nienow','15','RPG','/GameProfileImages/ac_valhalla.jpg');
values ('2','AC Oddysey','Assassins Creed Odyssey is an action role-playing video game developed by Ubisoft Quebec and published by Ubisoft. It is the eleventh major installment, and 21st overall, in the Assassins Creed series and the successor to 2017s Assassins Creed Origins. Principally set in the years 431ñ422 BC, the plot tells a mythological history of the Peloponnesian War between Athens and Sparta. Players control a male or female mercenary (Ancient Greek: ÏﬂÛËÈÔÚ misthios) who fights on both sides of the conflict as they attempt to find their family.',to_date('05/02/14','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/ACOdyssey.png','7','13','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','2','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','1','Videos/AcOdyssey.mp4','Schowalter, Steuber and Tromp','15','RPG','/GameProfileImages/ac_odyssey.jpg');
values ('3','Among Us','Among Us is a 2018 online multiplayer social deduction game developed and published by American game studio Innersloth. It was released on iOS and Android devices in June 2018 and on Windows in November 2018, featuring cross-platform play between these platforms. The game was also ported for the Nintendo Switch in December 2020, and has planned releases for the Xbox One, Xbox Series X and Series S, PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5 in 2021. The game was inspired by the party game Mafia and the science fiction horror film The Thing, and since the release of its first map, The Skeld, 3 other maps including MIRA HQ and Polus were introduced. Lastly the fourth map, "The Airship" based on Henry Stickmins Infiltrating the Airship was released in March 2021.',to_date('05/12/10','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/Among_us.png','2','14','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','4','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/AmongUs.mp4','Corwin-Kub','15','Mystery','/GameProfileImages/among_us.jpg');
values ('4','Apex Legends','Apex Legends is a free-to-play hero battle royale game developed by Respawn Entertainment and published by Electronic Arts. It was released for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One in February 2019, and for Nintendo Switch in March 2021. The game supports cross-platform play. The game is set in the same science fiction universe as Respawn Entertainments Titanfall series. A mobile version of the game specially designed for touchscreens titled Apex Legends Mobile has also been announced which is scheduled to be fully released by 2022 on Android and iOS.',to_date('19/11/16','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/ApexLegends.jpg','7','44','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','9','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/ApexLegends.mp4','Hickle-Kassulke','15','FPS','/GameProfileImages/apex.jpg');
values ('5','Call of Duty: MW2','Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 is a 2009 first-person shooter game developed by Infinity Ward and published by Activision. It is the sixth installment in the Call of Duty series and the direct sequel to Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare, continuing the storyline. It was released worldwide on November 10, 2009, for Microsoft Windows, the PlayStation 3, and Xbox 360. A separate version for the Nintendo DS, titled Modern Warfare: Mobilized, was also released on the same day. A version for macOS was developed by Aspyr and released in May 2014, and the Xbox 360 version was made backward compatible for the Xbox One in 2018.',to_date('17/04/13','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/cod_mw2.jpg','9','16','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','8','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/cod_mw2.mp4','Schroeder Inc','15','FPS','/GameProfileImages/cod_mw2.jpg');
values ('6','Control','Control is a 2019 action-adventure video game developed by Remedy Entertainment and published by 505 Games. Control was released in August 2019 for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One. A cloud-based version for the Nintendo Switch was released in October 2020. The versions for PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S were released in February 2021. The game revolves around the Federal Bureau of Control (FBC), a secret U.S. government agency tasked with containing and studying phenomena that violate the laws of reality. ',to_date('11/08/17','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/Control.png','1','68','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','6','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/Control.mp4','Goyette, Bode and Robel','15','RPG','/GameProfileImages/control.jpg');
values ('7','Counter Strike: GO','Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS:GO) is a multiplayer first-person shooter developed by Valve and Hidden Path Entertainment. It is the fourth game in the Counter-Strike series. Developed for over two years, Global Offensive was released for Windows, macOS, Xbox 360, and PlayStation 3 in August 2012, and for Linux in 2014. Valve still regularly updates the game, both with smaller balancing patches and larger content additions.',to_date('20/11/20','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/Counter_Strike.jpg','4','2','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','5','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/cs_go.mp4','Farrell-Rath','15','FPS','/GameProfileImages/cs_go.jpg');
values ('8','Crash Bandicoot 4','Crash Bandicoot 4: Its About Time is a 2020 platform game developed by Toys for Bob and published by Activision. The game is the eighth main installment in the Crash Bandicoot series and a retcon of the games that originally followed Crash Bandicoot: Warped. The games story follows Crash Bandicoot and his sister Coco, aided by their former enemy Dingodile and an alternate-dimension counterpart of Crashs old girlfriend Tawna, as they recover the all-powerful Quantum Masks in a bid to prevent Doctor Neo Cortex and Doctor Nefarious Tropy from taking over the multiverse.',to_date('27/03/10','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/crash.png','7','56','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','3','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/Crash4.mp4','Towne and Sons','15','Adventure','/GameProfileImages/crash.jpg');
values ('9','Detroit: Become Human','Detroit: Become Human is a 2018 adventure game developed by Quantic Dream and published by Sony Interactive Entertainment. The plot follows three androids: Kara (Valorie Curry), who escapes her owner to explore her newfound sentience and protect a young girl; Connor (Bryan Dechart), whose job is to hunt down sentient androids; and Markus (Jesse Williams), who devotes himself to releasing other androids from servitude.',to_date('13/07/14','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/Detroit_become_human.png','9','80','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','2','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/Detroit.mp4','Von-Mayert','15','Telltale','/GameProfileImages/detroit.jpg');
values ('10','Fortnite','Fortnite is an online video game developed by Epic Games and released in 2017. It is available in three distinct game mode versions that otherwise share the same general gameplay and game engine: Fortnite: Save the World, a cooperative hybrid-tower defense-shooter-survival game for up to four players to fight off zombie-like creatures and defend objects with traps and fortifications they can build; Fortnite Battle Royale, a free-to-play battle royale game in which up to 100 players fight to be the last person standing; and Fortnite Creative, in which players are given complete freedom to create worlds and battle arenas',to_date('09/04/18','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/Fortnite.png','1','37','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','8','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','1','Videos/Fortnite.mp4','Hintz LLC','15','FPS','/GameProfileImages/fortnite.jpg');
values ('11','Grand Theft Auto V','Grand Theft Auto V is a 2013 action-adventure game developed by Rockstar North and published by Rockstar Games. It is the first main entry in the Grand Theft Auto series since 2008s Grand Theft Auto IV. Set within the fictional state of San Andreas, based on Southern California, the single-player story follows three protagonistsóretired bank robber Michael De Santa, street gangster Franklin Clinton, and drug dealer and arms smuggler Trevor Philipsóand their efforts to commit heists while under pressure from a corrupt government agency and powerful criminals. The open world design lets players freely roam San Andreas open countryside and the fictional city of Los Santos, based on Los Angeles.',to_date('20/05/18','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/Grand_Theft_Auto_V.png','7','86','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','10','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/GtaV.mp4','Jacobson, Prosacco and Kiehn','15','Action','/GameProfileImages/gtaV.jpg');
values ('12','Grand Theft Auto IV','Grand Theft Auto IV is a 2008 action-adventure game developed by Rockstar North and published by Rockstar Games. It is the first main entry in the Grand Theft Auto series since 2004s Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas. Set within the fictional Liberty City, based on New York City, the single-player story follows Eastern European war veteran Niko Bellic and his attempts to escape his past while under pressure from loan sharks and mob bosses. The open world design lets players freely roam Liberty City, consisting of three main islands.',to_date('25/07/13','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/GTAIV.png','2','58','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','5','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','1','Videos/GtaIV.mp4','Abernathy Group','15','Action','/GameProfileImages/gtaIV.jpg');
values ('13','Half Life 2','Half-Life 2 is a 2004 first-person shooter game developed and published by Valve. Like the original Half-Life (1998), it combines shooting, puzzles, and storytelling, and adds features such as vehicles and physics-based gameplay. Players control Gordon Freeman, who fights the alien Combine with allies including resistance fighter Alyx Vance, using weapons such as the object-manipulating gravity gun.',to_date('13/10/19','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/Half_Life_2.png','9','99','Intel core i5 4rth GenIntel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','7','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','1','Videos/HalfLife2.mp4','Senger-Homenick','15','FPS','/GameProfileImages/half_life_2.jpg');
values ('14','Horizon Zero Dawn','Horizon Zero Dawn is a 2017 action role-playing game developed by Guerrilla Games and published by Sony Interactive Entertainment. The plot follows Aloy, a young hunter in a world overrun by machines, who sets out to uncover her past. The player uses ranged weapons, a spear, and stealth to combat mechanical creatures and other enemy forces. A skill tree provides the player with new abilities and bonuses. The player can explore the open world to discover locations and take on side quests. It was released for the PlayStation 4 in 2017 and Microsoft Windows in 2020.',to_date('22/02/21','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/Horizon_Zero_Dawn_cover.jpg','1','60','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','10','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/Horizon.mp4','Kohler LLC','15','RPG','/GameProfileImages/horizon.jpg');
values ('15','League of Legends','League of Legends (LoL), commonly referred to as League, is a 2009 multiplayer online battle arena video game developed and published by Riot Games. Inspired by Defense of the Ancients, a custom map for Warcraft III, Riots founders sought to develop a stand-alone game in the same genre. Since its release in October 2009, the game has been free-to-play and is monetized through purchasable character customization. The game is available for Microsoft Windows and macOS.',to_date('14/01/17','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/League of legends.png','2','81','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','5','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','1','Videos/lol.mp4','Jerde and Sons','15','MOBA','/GameProfileImages/lol.jpg');
values ('16','Rainbow Six Siege','Tom Clancys Rainbow Six Siege is an online tactical shooter video game developed by Ubisoft Montreal and published by Ubisoft. It was released worldwide for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One on December 1, 2015; the game was also released for PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S exactly five years later on December 1, 2020. The game puts heavy emphasis on environmental destruction and cooperation between players. Each player assumes control of an attacker or a defender in different gameplay modes such as rescuing a hostage, defusing a bomb, and taking control of an objective within a room. The title has no campaign but features a series of short, offline missions called, "situations" that can be played solo. ',to_date('18/10/20','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/rainbowsix.jpg','3','43','Intel core i5 4rth GenIntel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','6','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/r6.mp4','Anderson, Bernier and Runolfsdottir','15','FPS','/GameProfileImages/r6.jpg');
values ('17','Skyrim','The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim is an open world action role-playing video game developed by Bethesda Game Studios and published by Bethesda Softworks. It is the fifth main installment in The Elder Scrolls series, following 2006s The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion, and was released worldwide for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 3, and Xbox 360 on November 11, 2011.The games main story revolves around the players character, the Dragonborn, on their quest to defeat Alduin the World-Eater, a dragon who is prophesied to destroy the world. The game is set 200 years after the events of Oblivion and takes place in Skyrim, the northernmost province of Tamriel. ',to_date('15/11/17','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/skyrim.jpg','8','7','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','5','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','1','Videos/Skyrim.mp4','Cronin LLC','15','RPG','/GameProfileImages/skyrim.jpg');
values ('18','War robots','War Robots (previously titled Walking War Robots) is mobile app game developed and published by the Russian game developer Pixonic. It is a third-person shooter with real-time PvP battles in Multiplayer Online Battle Arena (MOBA) mode. Players operate BattleTech-like robots on a live battlefield. They either have the option to play solo or team up with other players. It was first released on iOS in 2014 and was released to Android the following year.',to_date('05/08/20','DD/MM/RR'),'/poster/war_robots.png','10','55','Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300','Windows 7 or newer','4','NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB / AMD Radeon R7 370 2GB','0','Videos/warRobots.mp4','Bailey-Terry','15','RPG','/GameProfileImages/war_robots.jpg');


